response.overview: Understanding What Legacy Means to America | Made to Last In this original documentary, VICE in partnership with Dickies, examines the real stories of American grit, culture and identity through the eyes of a modernizing rancher, a Chicana third-generation mechanic, and a brotherhood of southern skateboarders. These communities, like Dickies, are passionate about holding on to their legacy while plotting the future. Dickies champions the dignity of work and instills confidence in the makers and shapers of our world.
response.title: DICKIES - MADE TO LAST
